{"title":"vielö","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003evielö is a multi-award-winning, sustainable (circular production) and genuinely organic (not just natural) skincare alternative for design lovers. vielö stands for “the best of both worlds”, uncompromising organic quality married with a minimalist design and lifestyle. All vielö products are locally produced, certified organic and sustainably made, based on refined liquid organic whey. Thanks to the skin-friendly whey, all vielö products are super gentle and nourishing, making them also particularly suitable for dry and sensitive skin. We never use controversial and\/or disputed ingredients such as sulphates which are still widespread even amongst the so-called natural skincare industry. vielö products never dry out the skin instead they nourish the skin in a natural way. No controversial ingredients, no greenwashing, no misleading instead authentic skin and body care of the highest organic quality and for people who simply expect more from a brand than just a nice label.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","products":[{"product_id":"organic-body-lotion-250ml","title":"Vielö Organic Body Lotion 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNourishing organic body lotion, specially designed to moisturise and soften dry and sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), wheat germ oil (protecting), hyaluronic acid (hydrating), organic extracts of calendula (regenerating), lavender (soothing) and sage (strengthening).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSuitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake well before use. Apply to clean and dry skin. Massage in gently.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Lactis Serum Proteinum **, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil **, Triticum Vulgare Germ Oil **, Polyglyceryl-3 Dicitrate \/ Stearate *, Cetyl Alcohol *, Glycerin **, Betaine *, Aqua *, Citric Acid *, Xanthan Gum *, Tocopherol *, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil **, Sodium Hyaluronate *, Potassium Sorbate, Salvia Officinalis Oil **, Citronellol ** \/ ***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil **, Geraniol ** \/ ***, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate *, Arnica Montana Flower Extract **, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract **, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract **, Limonene ** \/ ***, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract **, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract **, Sodium Lactate *, Citral ** \/ ***.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (89,7%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products. \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49091771334983,"sku":"","price":42.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-body-lotion-250ml-512663.jpg?v=1739897339"},{"product_id":"copy-of-organic-body-wash-250ml-1","title":"Vielö Organic Body Wash 250ml","description":"\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNourishing organic body wash, specially designed to cleanse, nourish and moisturise dry and sensitive skin gently.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), wheat protein (moisturising), soy protein (strengthening) and organic extracts of arnica (soothing), birch leaf (purifying) and rosemary (stimulating).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSuitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake well before use. Apply to wet skin. Leave on briefly. Rinse thoroughly.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003cu\u003e:\u003c\/u\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Aqua*, Glycerin**, Decyl Glucoside*, Disodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Xanthan Gum*, Betaine*, Polyglyceryl-3 Caprate*, Citric Acid*, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Potassium Sorbate, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein*, Hydrolyzed Wheat Gluten*, Citronellol**\/***, Hydrolyzed Soy Protein*, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Geraniol**\/***, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Arnica Montana Flower Extract**, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract**, Caesalpinia Spinosa Gum*, Betula Alba Leaf Extract**, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Lactate*, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Benzoate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (68,3%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49091841130823,"sku":null,"price":27.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-body-wash-250ml-637632.jpg?v=1739897340"},{"product_id":"organic-hand-wash-250ml","title":"Vielö Organic Hand Wash 250ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNourishing organic hand wash, specially designed to cleanse gently while leaving the hands soft and smooth.\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), soy protein (strengthening) and organic extracts of lavender (soothing), nettle (antioxidant) and rosemary (stimulating).\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSuitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake well before use. Dispense into wet hands. Rinse thoroughly. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Aqua*, Glycerin**, Decyl Glucoside*, Disodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Betaine*, Polyglyceryl-3 Caprate*, Xanthan Gum*, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Citric Acid*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Potassium Sorbate, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Geraniol**\/***, Hydrolyzed Soy Protein*, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Sodium Lactate*, Caesalpinia Spinosa Gum*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract**, Urtica Dioica Leaf Extract**, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Benzoate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e** certified organic (67,5%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products. \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49091863740743,"sku":null,"price":23.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-hand-wash-250ml-158204.jpg?v=1739897343"},{"product_id":"copy-of-organic-hand-wash-250ml","title":"Vielö Organic Hand Balm 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNourishing organic hand balm, specially designed to moisturise and soften dry and sensitive hands.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), wheat germ oil (protecting), hyaluronic acid (hydrating), organic extracts of calendula (regenerating), lavender (soothing) and sage (strengthening).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSuitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eShake well before use. Dispense into hands. Massage gently. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil**, Triticum Vulgare Germ Oil**, Polyglyceryl-3 Dicitrate \/Stearate*, Cetyl Alcohol*, Glycerin**, Betaine*, Aqua*, Citric Acid*, Xanthan Gum*, Tocopherol*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Sodium Hyaluronate*, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Potassium Sorbate, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Geraniol**\/***, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract**, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Limonene**\/***, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract**, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Lactate*, Citral**\/***.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e** certified organic (88,9%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*** from natural essential oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"product__description rte quick-add-hidden\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49091902308679,"sku":null,"price":20.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-hand-balm-50ml-856976.jpg?v=1739897346"},{"product_id":"organic-cleansing-milk-100ml","title":"Vielö Organic Cleansing Milk 100ml","description":"\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eGentle organic cleansing milk to remove make-up and dirt effortlessly. Soothes the skin, leaving it soft and hydrated.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), organic wheat germ oil (nurturing), organic rosehip seed oil (soothing) and organic extracts of chamomile (antiseptic), arnica (anti-inflammatory) and sage (antibacterial).\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSuitable for all skin types, also for dry and sensitive skin.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to Use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Massage gently into dry skin across face and neck. Rinse with lukewarm water. Use it in the morning and evening and whenever your skin needs natural cleansing. Shake before use.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-mce-fragment=\"1\" class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Lactis Serum Proteinum**, Rosa Canina Fruit Oil**, Prunus Armeniaca Kernel Oil**, Polyglyceryl-3 Dicitrate\/Stearate*, Glycerin**, Triticum Vulgare (Wheat) Germ Oil**, Aqua*, Cetyl Alcohol*, Sodium Levulinate*, Glyceryl Caprylate*, Citric Acid*, Xanthan Gum*, Sodium Anisate, Tocopherol*, Lavandula Angusti- folia Flower Oil**, Potassium Sorbate, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil**, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Citronellol**\/***, Pelar- gonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Matricaria Chamomilla Flower Extract**, Arnica Montana Flower Extract**, Geraniol**\/***, Sodium Lactate*, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract**, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Limonene**\/***, Citral**\/***.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from natural origin (99,7%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (87,1%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49092148592967,"sku":null,"price":32.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-cleansing-milk-100ml-720327.jpg?v=1739897336"},{"product_id":"organic-toner-100ml","title":"Vielö Organic Toner 100ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eNourishing \u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eorganic toner to gently soothe, refresh and cleanse the skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCreated with o\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003erganic whey (nourishing), organic witch hazel water (nurturing), hyaluronic acid (hydrating) and organic extracts of calendula (regenerating), mallow (protecting) and chamomile (antiseptic).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSuitable for all skin types, also for dry and sensitive skin. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake well before use. Splash into hands and massage gently into face and neck or spray directly onto face. Use it in the morning and evening and whenever your skin needs refreshing hydration. Use before applying a moisturizer. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Lactis Serum Proteinum **, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil **, Triticum Vulgare Germ Oil **, Polyglyceryl-3 Dicitrate \/ Stearate *, Cetyl Alcohol *, Glycerin **, Betaine *, Aqua *, Citric Acid *, Xanthan Gum *, Tocopherol *, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil **, Sodium Hyaluronate *, Potassium Sorbate, Salvia Officinalis Oil **, Citronellol ** \/ ***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil **, Geraniol ** \/ ***, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate *, Arnica Montana Flower Extract **, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract **, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract **, Limonene ** \/ ***, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract **, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract **, Sodium Lactate *, Citral ** \/ ***.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e* from natural origin (99,7%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e** certified organic (87,1%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products. \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49092182901063,"sku":null,"price":34.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-toner-100ml-558653.jpg?v=1739897335"},{"product_id":"organic-hyaluron-serum-50ml","title":"Vielö Organic Hyaluron Serum 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIntensely nourishing organic hyaluron serum to deliver long- lasting moisture and to strengthen the skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), hyaluronic acid (hydrating) and organic extracts of calendula (regenerating), rose hip (anti-inflammatory) and eyebright (strengthening).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all skin types, also for dry and sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to Use\u003c\/strong\u003e: Shake well before use. In the morning and evening apply 1-2 drops on the hands and gently tap into cleansed face and neck.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Aqua*, Glycerin**, Betaine*, Sodium Levulinate*, Xanthan Gum*, Glyceryl Caprylate*, Sodium Hyaluronate*, Sodium Anisate, Potassium Sorbate, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Citronellol**\/***, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Citric Acid*, Euphrasia Officinalis Extract**, Rosa Canina Fruit Ex- tract**, Sodium Lactate*, Geraniol**\/***, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract**, Limonene**\/***, Citral**\/***.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from natural origin (99,7%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (93,2%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49092215341383,"sku":null,"price":69.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-hyaluron-serum-50ml-505516.jpg?v=1739897339"},{"product_id":"organic-eye-cream-15ml","title":"Vielö Organic Eye Cream 15ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNourishing organic eye cream to deliver long-lasting hydration and effectively nurture the delicate skin around the eyes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), organic rosehip seed oil (soothing), hyaluronic acid (hydrating), organic sunflower oil (nurturing) and organic extracts of camomile (invigorating), eyebright (strengthening) and mallow (protecting).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSuitable for all skin types, also for dry and sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake well before use. Apply to clean and dry skin. Massage in gently. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Rosa Canina Fruit Oil**, Polyglyceryl-3 Dicitrate\/ Stearate*, Glycerin**, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil**, Cetyl Alcohol*, Aqua*, Prunus Armeniaca Kernel Oil**, Triticum Vulgare (Wheat) Germ Oil**, Sodium Levulinate*, Glyceryl Caprylate*, Sodium Hyaluronate*, Xanthan Gum*, Sodium Anisate, Tocopherol*, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid*, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Matricaria Chamomilla Flower Extract**, Malva Sylvestris Leaf Extract**, Euphrasia Officinalis Extract**, Sodium Lactate*, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Limonene**\/***, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Geraniol**\/***, Citral**\/***.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e* from natural origin (99,7%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e** certified organic (87,1%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products. \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49093397217607,"sku":null,"price":47.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-eye-cream-15ml-750536.jpg?v=1739897336"},{"product_id":"organic-day-cream-50ml","title":"Vielö Organic Day Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eNourishing organic day cream to deliver long-lasting hydration, leaving the skin soft and smooth.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), hyaluronic acid (hydrating), organic apricot kernel oil (nurturing) and organic extracts of chamomile (soothing), pansy (protecting) and arnica (anti-inflammatory).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSuitable for all skin types, also for dry and sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to Use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Massage gently into freshly cleansed skin and neck. Use it in the morning and evening and whenever your skin needs natural hydration. Perfect as make-up base.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Lactis Serum Proteinum**, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate*, Prunus Armeniaca Kernel Oil**, Glycerin**, Aqua*, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil**, Cetyl Alcohol*, Rosa Canina Fruit Oil**, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter**, Sodium Levulinate*, Glyceryl Caprylate*, Sodium Hyaluronate*, Xanthan Gum*, Sodium Anisate, Tocopherol*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid*, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Viola Tricolor Extract**, Malva Sylvestris Flower Extract**, Arnica Montana Flower Extract**, Matricaria Chamomilla Flower Extract**, Geraniol**\/***, Sodium Lactate*, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Limonene**\/***, Citral**\/***.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e* from natural origin (99,7%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e** certified organic (85,3%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49093435031879,"sku":null,"price":52.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-day-cream-50ml-714190.jpg?v=1739897338"},{"product_id":"organic-night-cream-50ml","title":"Vielö Organic Night Cream 50ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eRich organic night cream to intensely hydrate and nourish the skin overnight and stimulate skin regeneration.\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), rosehip seed oil (soothing), hyaluronic acid (hydrating), wheat germ oil (protecting) and organic extracts of chamomile (antiseptic), arnica (anti-inflammatory) and mallow (protecting).\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003eSuitable for all skin types, also for dry and sensitive skin.\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to Use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Massage gently into freshly cleansed skin and neck. Use it in the evening and whenever your skin needs rich hydration.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Lactis Serum Proteinum**, Rosa Canina Fruit Oil**, Triticum Vulgare (Wheat) Germ Oil**, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil**, Glycerin**, Cera Alba**, Polyglyceryl-3 Polyricinoleate*, Aqua*, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter**, Sorbitan Sesquioleate*, Oenothera Biennis Oil**, Sodium Levulinate*, Glyceryl Caprylate*, Polyglyceryl-3 Ricinoleate, Sodium Hyaluronate*, Sodium Anisate, Tocopherol*, Citric Acid*, Potassium Sorbate, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Malva Sylvestris Flower Extract**, Viola Tricolor Extract**, Matricaria Chamomilla Flower Extract**, Arnica Montana Flower Extract**, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Geraniol**\/***, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Lactate*, Limonene**\/***, Citral**\/***.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e* from natural origin (99,3%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e** certified organic (89,2%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-fragment=\"1\"\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products. \u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49093459968327,"sku":null,"price":59.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-night-cream-50ml-212703.jpg?v=1739897344"},{"product_id":"vielo-organic-shampoo-250ml","title":"Vielö Organic Shampoo 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNourishing organic shampoo, specially designed to cleanse, repair and moisturise damaged hair and sensitive scalps gently.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), black oats (moisturising), soy protein (strengthening) and organic extracts of lavender (soothing), nettle (antioxidant) and rosemary (stimulating).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all hair types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake well before use. Apply to wet hair. Massage gently into hair and on scalp. Rinse thoroughly.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Aqua*, Glycerin**, Decyl Glucoside*, Disodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Xanthan Gum*, Betaine*, Polyglyceryl-3 Caprate*, Citric Acid*, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Hydrolyzed Wheat Gluten*, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein*, Potassium Sorbate, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Citronellol**\/***, Hydrolyzed Soy Protein*, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Geraniol**\/***, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Lecithin*, Avena Strigosa Seed Extract*, Malva Sylvestris Flower Extract**, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract**, Caesalpinia Spinosa Gum*, Urtica Dioica Leaf Extract**, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Lactate*, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Benzoate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (68,1%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50900996653383,"sku":null,"price":30.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-shampoo-250ml-599294.webp?v=1739897169"},{"product_id":"vielo-organic-conditioner-250ml","title":"Vielö Organic Conditioner 250ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNourishing organic conditioner, specially designed to strengthen and moisturise damaged hair, leaving it soft and smooth.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), soy extract (invigorating), wheat germ oil (protecting), organic extracts of lavender (soothing), sage (strengthening) and mallow (moisturising).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all hair types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply after shampooing to wet hair. Massage gently into hair and on scalp. Rinse thoroughly.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Triticum Vulgare Germ Oil**, Polyglyceryl-3 Dicitrate\/Stearate*, Cetyl Alcohol*, Glycerin**, Aqua*, Betaine*, Citric Acid*, Xanthan Gum*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Tocopherol*, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil**, Potassium Sorbate, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Geraniol**\/***, Malva Sylvestris Flower Extract**, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract**, Glycine Soja Seed Extract*, Urtica Dioica Leaf Extract**, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Lactate*, Sodium Benzoate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (88,9%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50901055078727,"sku":null,"price":32.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-conditioner-250ml-654164.jpg?v=1739897176"},{"product_id":"vielo-organic-body-scrub-50ml","title":"Vielö Organic Body Scrub 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNourishing organic body scrub, specially designed to cleanse and exfoliate the skin gently, to remove dead skin cells and revitalise your body.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), finely ground apricot kernels (exfoliating), wheat germ oil (moisturising), organic extracts of birch leaf (purifying), lavender (soothing) and rosemary (stimulating).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake well before use. Apply to damp skin. In circular movement massage in gently. Rinse off thoroughly. On contact with water and by gently massaging in, the scrub transforms into a nourishing lotion that can be washed off easily.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Glycerin**, Aqua*, Decyl Glucoside*, Prunus Armeniaca Seed Powder**, Triticum Vulgare Germ Oil**, Citric Acid*, Betaine*, Xanthan Gum*, Disodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Potassium Sorbate, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Geraniol**\/***, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract**, Betula Alba Leaf Extract**, Glycine Soja Seed Extract*, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Lactate*, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Benzoate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (74,9%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50901064843591,"sku":null,"price":19.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-body-scrub-50ml-231547.webp?v=1739897173"},{"product_id":"vielo-organic-facial-scrub-50ml","title":"Vielö Organic Facial Scrub 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGentle organic facial scrub to effectively cleanse and remove dead skin cells, leaving the skin soft and refreshed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMade with o\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003erganic whey (nourishing), finely ground apricot kernels (exfoliating), hyaluronic acid (hydrating), organic wheat germ oil (nurturing) and organic extracts of camomile (antiseptic), rose hip (anti-inflammatory) and marigold (regenerating).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all skin types, also for dry and sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Massage gently into dry and clean skin. Moisten fingertips with warm water and massage again till the scrub turns into a white creamy texture. Rinse off with lukewarm water. Use 1-2 times per week.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Glycerin**, Triticum Vulgare (Wheat) Germ Oil**, Prunus Armeniaca Seed Powder**, Aqua*, Xanthan Gum*, Kaolin*, Sodium Levulinate*, Glyceryl Caprylate*, Sodium Anisate, Potassium Sorbate, Citric Acid*, Sodium Hyaluronate*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Rosa Canina Fruit Extract**, Matricaria Chamomilla Flower Extract**, Sodium Lactate*, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract**.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from natural origin (99,7%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (92,7%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50901084832071,"sku":null,"price":37.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-facial-scrub-50ml-749873.jpg?v=1739897173"},{"product_id":"vielo-organic-facial-masque-50ml","title":"Vielö Organic Facial Masque 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePurifying organic mask to gently yet effectively cleanse, soothe and hydrate the skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMade with organic whey (nourishing), white clay (purifying), hyaluronic acid (hydrating), organic witch hazel water (nurturing), organic rosehip seed oil (soothing), and organic extracts of calendula (regenerating), cucumber (refreshing) and mallow (protecting).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all skin types, also for dry and sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply a generous layer to clean face and neck. Leave for 15 minutes until dry. Rinse gently with warm water. Use once or twice a week.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Hamamelis Virginiana Water**, Rosa Canina Fruit Oil**, Glyceryl Stearate Citrate*, Cetyl Alcohol*, Glycerin**, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil**, Aqua*, Kaolin*, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter**, Triticum Vulgare (Wheat) Germ Oil**, Oenothera Biennis Oil**, Sodium Levulinate*, Glyceryl Caprylate*, Sodium Hyaluronate*, Citric Acid*, Xanthan Gum*, Sodium Anisate, Tocopherol*, Potassium Sorbate, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract**, Cucumis Sativus Fruit Extract**, Malva Sylvestris Flower Extract**, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract**, Sodium Lactate*.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (81,7%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50901095088455,"sku":null,"price":40.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-facial-masque-50ml-901935.jpg?v=1739897176"},{"product_id":"vielo-organic-foot-balm-50ml","title":"Vielö Organic Foot  Balm 50ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNourishing organic foot balm, specially designed to moisturise and soften dry feet and cracked heels.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), wheat germ oil (protecting), hyaluronic acid (hydrating), organic extracts of calendula (regenerating), lavender (soothing) and sage (strengthening).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply to clean and dry skin and massage in well. Regular use helps to protect the skin from drying out.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/span\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil**, Triticum Vulgare Germ Oil**, Polyglyceryl-3 Dicitrate \/Stearate*, Cetyl Alcohol*, Glycerin**, Betaine*, Aqua*, Citric Acid*, Xanthan Gum*, Tocopherol*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Sodium Hyaluronate*, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Potassium Sorbate, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Geraniol**\/***, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract**, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Limonene**\/***, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract**, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Lactate*, Citral**\/***.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (88,9%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oil\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50901104427335,"sku":null,"price":20.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-foot-balm-50ml-911694.jpg?v=1739897171"},{"product_id":"vielo-organic-body-lotion-refill-500ml","title":"Vielö Organic Body Lotion Refill 500ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNourishing organic body lotion, specially designed to moisturise and soften dry and sensitive skin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), wheat germ oil (protecting), hyaluronic acid (hydrating), organic extracts of calendula (regenerating), lavender (soothing) and sage (strengthening).\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSuitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBy choosing sustainable refills you take good care of your skin and our planet.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake well before use. Apply to clean and dry skin. Massage in gently.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Lactis Serum Proteinum **, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil **, Triticum Vulgare Germ Oil **, Polyglyceryl-3 Dicitrate \/ Stearate *, Cetyl Alcohol *, Glycerin **, Betaine *, Aqua *, Citric Acid *, Xanthan Gum *, Tocopherol *, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil **, Sodium Hyaluronate *, Potassium Sorbate, Salvia Officinalis Oil **, Citronellol ** \/ ***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil **, Geraniol ** \/ ***, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate *, Arnica Montana Flower Extract **, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract **, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract **, Limonene ** \/ ***, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract **, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract **, Sodium Lactate *, Citral ** \/ ***.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003cbr\u003e** certified organic (89,7%)\u003cbr\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50901107507527,"sku":null,"price":70.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-body-lotion-refill-500ml-719231.jpg?v=1739897176"},{"product_id":"vielo-organic-hand-wash-refill-500ml","title":"Vielö Organic Hand Wash Refill 500ml","description":"\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNourishing organic hand wash, specially designed to cleanse gently while leaving the hands soft and smooth.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eCreated with organic whey (nourishing), soy protein (strengthening) and organic extracts of lavender (soothing), nettle (antioxidant) and rosemary (stimulating).\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eSuitable for all skin types.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBy choosing sustainable refills you take good care of your skin and our planet. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Shake well before use. Dispense into wet hands. Rinse thoroughly. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"content-translations text-15 leading-loose text-black\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eLactis Serum Proteinum**, Aqua*, Glycerin**, Decyl Glucoside*, Disodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Betaine*, Polyglyceryl-3 Caprate*, Xanthan Gum*, Sodium Cocoyl Glutamate*, Citric Acid*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Oil**, Salvia Officinalis Oil**, Potassium Sorbate, Citronellol**\/***, Pelargonium Graveolens Flower Oil**, Geraniol**\/***, Hydrolyzed Soy Protein*, Polyglyceryl-4 Caprate*, Sodium Lactate*, Caesalpinia Spinosa Gum*, Lavandula Angustifolia Flower Extract**, Urtica Dioica Leaf Extract**, Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Salvia Officinalis Leaf Extract**, Sodium Benzoate.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e* from natural origin (99,8%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e** certified organic (67,5%)\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*** from natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Austria\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eInspired by circular economy, Vielö refines a high-quality by-product of cheese production, liquid organic whey, and uses it to create certified organic and sustainable skin and body care products.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"vielö","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50901114716487,"sku":null,"price":39.0,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/vielo-organic-hand-wash-refill-500ml-257750.jpg?v=1739897189"}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/collections\/vielo-433434.jpg?v=1739897069","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/collections\/vielo.oembed","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}